	<desc><![CDATA[<p>Walk along a chalk ridge to the sea finishing along the Seven Sisters cliffs</p><p>This route was created by the Saturday Walkers Club. It is fully written up at <a href="https://www.walkingclub.org.uk/long-distance-path/south-downs-way/">https://www.walkingclub.org.uk/long-distance-path/south-downs-way/</a> #swcwalks</p><p> COPYRIGHT 2025 SATURDAY WALKERS CLUB ANDREW MURPHY ALL RIGHTS RESERVED WWW.WALKINGCLUB.ORG.UK </p>]]></desc>
